                        <interp inst="t18530228-name-330" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES HART</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, E</hi> 99). I produce a certificate (<hi rend="italic">read: <persName id="t18530228-name-331">
                        <interp inst="t18530228-name-331" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
