                  </hi>, alias <hi rend="italic">George Kipling, convicted here, Feb.</hi> 1849, <hi rend="italic">having been before convicted; confined one year</hi>)—Kipling is the same person.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
