                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, E</hi> 51). I produce a certificate (<hi rend="italic">read: <persName id="t18530228-name-333">
                        <interp inst="t18530228-name-333" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18530228-name-333" type="surname" value="LEWIS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18530228-name-333" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>Edward Lewis</persName>
                  </hi>, alias <hi rend="italic">
                     <persName id="t18530228-name-334">
