                        <interp inst="t18530228-name-334" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>John Brown</persName>, convicted here, Nov.</hi> 1849, <hi rend="italic">having been before convicted; confined nine months—Smith</hi> is the person there described.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">KIPLING</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
GUILTY</hi>. Aged 23.</p>
